和研学旅行，使学生掌握现代地球科学的思想和方法，培养创新思维、科学精神和生存技能。周忠和委员：中学地理课亟须升级为地球科学课 ---2023 年全国两会专题 (cas.cn)"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-c09a0a9414afb37f262c1fe717ea5d3b_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "87 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/588034994"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I4srJ5oTMxMBREAMaCDkyOTU2MjM0IK/LmqAGMAE4LUARcgk1ODgwMzQ5OTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1678172863.2631452", "card_id": "Q_587444781", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为何存在打羽毛球输赢赌饮料这种嗜好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-25c83f1f74ce58321dadaecad2e7049a_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "82 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/587444781"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I4srJ5oTMxMBREAMaCDkyODI0Nzg1IKi3iaAGMAA4HEAScgk1ODc0NDQ3ODF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1678172863.2637808", "card_id": "Q_586890155", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 70}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何理解一个国家的「安全」？哪些时刻你曾感受到过这种「安全感」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "粮食安全、社会安全、科技安全、军事安全…一个国家的「安全」有多重要？有哪些时刻，你曾切身感受到过这种「安全感」？ 央视新闻联合知乎「知媒观察」发起「新开局，并肩出发」主题问答。 分享你的期待，有机会登上 @央视新闻 ！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-36f417a2a1842260b014a9d99ef98376_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "81 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"ty